          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_lvj_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/VariableList16.gif" id="image_r4x_qrn_ps"/>Insert
                Definition List</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a definition list (<xmlelement>dl</xmlelement> element) with one list item (a
